OL,3,CSchool dinners, taxis and music
OL,4,Clessons identified in education cost-
OL,5,Csaving bid
OL,7,FThe cost of school dinners in Northern
OL,8,FIreland is set to rise by 50p in the
OL,9,Fnew year as part of measures to
OL,10,Faddress the funding crisis in the
OL,11,Feducation sector.
OL,13,FOther measures include hiking music
OL,14,Flesson charges, cutting overtime,
OL,15,Fagency contracts and the use of
OL,16,Fexternal educational contractors.
OL,18,FThe Education Authority (EA) also
OL,19,Fraised concerns over the increasing
OL,20,Fcost of school taxis, which has almost
OL,21,Fdoubled in five years.
