OL,7,FThe EA, which manages schools in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, is facing a funding
OL,9,Fshortfall of around #300m. It is
OL,10,Fhoping to save around #30m from these
OL,11,Fmeasures.
OL,13,FIn a statement on Wednesday, it
OL,14,Fhighlighted that education services
OL,15,Fface "growing and increasingly
OL,16,Funsustainable budgetary shortfalls for
OL,17,Fa number of years".
