OL,7,FThe statement said: "We have been
OL,8,Fadvised that, unlike the position in
OL,9,Fprevious years, additional significant
OL,10,Ffunding allocations are unlikely to be
OL,11,Fmade available to address this
OL,12,Fshortfall.
OL,14,F"The Education Authority has therefore
OL,15,Fregrettably been required to identify
OL,16,Fa series of significant savings
OL,17,Fmeasures.
