OL,7,F"While these measures will inevitably
OL,8,Fhave an adverse impact on services, it
OL,9,Fis also the case that they can only
OL,10,Fmake a partial contribution to
OL,11,Fachieving a break-even budget."
OL,13,FThe statement outlined that more than
OL,14,F80% of its annual expenditure is on
OL,15,Fpayroll costs, including wages for
OL,16,Fteachers and support staff.
OL,18,FThe EA also said virtually all of its
OL,19,Fservices are statutory in nature and
OL,20,Fcannot therefore be lawfully stopped.
