OL,7,FIt said it had identified a number of
OL,8,Fmeasures which "have the potential to
OL,9,Frealise up to #30m in savings".
OL,11,FThese include savings in home to
OL,12,Fschool transport, including potential
OL,13,Frenegotiated payments to taxi operators
OL,15,FThe statement outlined how taxi use
OL,16,Fcost around #20m five years ago and
OL,17,Fwas almost #40m last year.
OL,19,F"The increasing cost of taxis is of
OL,20,Fsignificant concern to EA," the
OL,21,Fauthority said.
